data.description: Check out this great 2 story home in the Village of Greene with a nice blend of new and original features.  The eat-in kitchen has been freshly painted and has the original 9x4 butlers pantry offering ample kitchen storage. There is a nice-sized mudroom at the back entrance of the house. A large living room, dining area/entry, small bedroom/office, high ceilings, and an open floor plan complete the 1sth floor. Up the back stairs you'll find the loft room currently used as a bedroom, and 2 bedrooms accessible from the front stairs. The AMAZING 45x30 2-story garage is a bonus find in the village! The 2nd story of the garage is accessed by a full set of stairs which offers more work and storage space. Enjoy the summer from the deck or front porch, and have peace of mind with the FULLY FENCED yard. Affordable municipal electricity, Convenient to schools, Raymond Corporation, shopping, dining, and parks. This is a low-maintenance home, vinyl-sided, ready to move right into!
